1},{"word":"restaurant","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"must-haves","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"foods","count":1},{"word":"huaipu","count":1},{"word":"mining","count":1},{"word":"firm","count":1},{"word":"knowledgeable","count":1},{"word":"mineral","count":1},{"word":"expert","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"mithril","count":1},{"word":"clue","count":1},{"word":"fan","count":1},{"word":"name","count":1},{"word":"xieyang","count":1},{"word":"often","count":1},{"word":"institute","count":1},{"word":"daytime","count":1},{"word":"reservoir","count":1},{"word":"ideas","count":1},{"word":"generous","count":1},{"word":"providing","count":1},{"word":"suggestions","count":1},{"word":"easy","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"passion","count":1},{"word":"second","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"solaris","count":1},{"word":"conversations","count":1},{"word":"easier","count":1},{"word":"however","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"riddler","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"pretty","count":1},{"word":"confident","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"entrust","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Drinks that will prevail on foreign taste buds... Maybe I should do a street interview with those visitors?","quest_name":"Specialty Drinks","quest_id":880000004},{"text":"The Pioneer Merchandises have been Ganxue's staple. Many visitors bring one of those back as a gift.","quest_name":"Specialty Drinks","quest_id":880000004},{"text":"That would be a good idea that you ask Ganxue about their comments on Jinzhou.","quest_name":"Specialty Drinks","quest_id":880000004},{"text":"Speaking of the <color=highlight>Sea of Flowers</color>, I do visit Bogu's Arbor around the business area when off shift.","quest_name":"Sea of Flowers in the Valley","quest_id":880000005},{"text":"If you want to inquire about something related to plants, you can ask Grandma Lin, the owner there, for some information.","quest_name":"Sea of Flowers in the Valley","quest_id":880000005},{"text":"An entomologist... I have no clues.","quest_name":"Golden Insect","quest_id":880000006},{"text":"Maybe you should go to the pond. Some kids are frequently seen catching flies there.","quest_name":"Golden Insect","quest_id":880000006},{"text":"A ferocious opponent... The Crownless... Maybe you should ask someone who frequents the danger zone?","quest_name":"Crownless?","quest_id":880000007},{"text":"Xianchen over there is an experienced Pioneer explorer. If you need help, how about asking her?","quest_name":"Crownless?","quest_id":880000007},{"text":"Well, Panhua's Restaurant is definitely one of the must-haves in Jinzhou.","quest_name":"Unforgettable Dishes","quest_id":880000008},{"text":"If you need to learn about foods, I suggest you ask for Panhua's advice.","quest_name":"Unforgettable Dishes","quest_id":880000008},{"text":"Well, maybe you should ask the owner of Huaipu Mining Firm. He is a knowledgeable mineral expert.","quest_name":"Mithril","quest_id":880000009},{"text":"Since it's about the Mithril, I suggest you go ask for his advice.","quest_name":"Mithril","quest_id":880000009},{"text":"If you ask me, there is a clue you can get from one book fan.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"His name is Xieyang, often seen around the Jinzhou Institute during the daytime.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"He has a reservoir of ideas for this book, generous in providing suggestions. But...","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"His words are usually saddled with riddles.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"No, he is easy to get along with. But his words are usually saddled with riddles...","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"We all can tell his passion for <i>Second Coming of Solaris</i>, but that doesn't make our conversations easier.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"However, I have the feeling that you can understand him.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"Though I'm not sure if Riddler is the right word, you seem pretty confident in this.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010},{"text":"Then I'll entrust you to this.","quest_name":"Burning Jade","quest_id":880000010}]}